headline: Consumers Energy Defends Customer Protections for Data Centers Against Challenge from Attorney General
summary: Consumers Energy is standing up for Michigan and responsible economic growth in our state. The company is opposing a legal challenge from the state Attorney General that would undo new protections for customers as Michigan attracts data centers and other large businesses.
